author: @user-er8ii4fe1n
text:
Omg 14:26 that little giggle, Mina please stay happy, you are so beautiful. It really surprised me how hurt I was when I heard you had an anxiety disorder, I wish nothing but the best for you, Nayeon, Jeongyeon, Sana, Chaeyoung, Dahyun, Tzuyu, Momo and Jihyo. (feels rude to just say 'the other girls' so I gotta say everyone's names).

I was never really interested in Twice before this year, I don't know what led me to delve deeper into this group (probs the pandemic). So at first I wanted at least know their names so I memorized them, then that led me to funny videos, happy videos and even sad videos. Now knowing a bit of their past and how they got to where they are now, not a day goes by where I don't watch something Twice related, it's crazy. 

Everyone please keep sending them love and support, they are just amazing humans that don't deserve hate honestly, just remember all it takes is a few words from just one person to completely break someone.... I hope they stay together for a long time.
